Newsletter Automation Tools Comparison
A breakdown of the main tools used at each stage of an AI-assisted newsletter workflow.

:TASK
[ ] Perplexity: research and source aggregation
[ ] ChatGPT or Claude: draft generation and editing
[ ] Beehiiv: send platform with built-in growth tools
[ ] ConvertKit: strong for creator monetization workflows
[ ] Zapier: connect tools and trigger automations
[ ] Notion AI: topic planning and editorial calendar

:NOTE
Beehiiv and ConvertKit both offer free tiers. Start on free until you hit 500 subscribers, then evaluate which platform analytics suit your growth strategy.

